fileSamples.statement: (lbl : label) (instr : instruction) : if is_label lbl instr then instr = Llabel lbl else instr <> Llabel lbl.
fileSamples.proofString:
destruct instr; simpl; try discriminate.
case (peq lbl l); intro; congruence.

(lbl l : label) : if if peq lbl l then true else false
then Llabel l = Llabel lbl
else Llabel l <> Llabel lbl.
